<b>Errors</b> 
	<pre>Failure 4xx with proper error message
{
  &quot;code&quot; : &quot;developer.service.InvalidCompanyName&quot;,
  &quot;message&quot; : &quot;Invalid Company Name&quot;,
  &quot;contexts&quot; : [ ]
}</pre>

